    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior retains a strong shine, though you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the upholstery is in great shape, with only slight wear visible on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Mechanically, the car is solid\u2014it starts reliably, shifts smoothly, and has no known leaks or warning lights. It\u2019s an excellent choice for a buyer looking for a dependable, presentable vehicle that is ready for the road without needing immediate repairs.",
      "price": 32500.0,
