    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of uncompromising caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable showroom condition, having been preserved to the highest standards of stewardship. Every detail, from the pristine interior surfaces to the flawless exterior finish, adheres to original factory specifications. This represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a definitive example of the model, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from new.",
